graph LR
    KubeRay[KubeRay Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    KubeRay -->|orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.25+]
    KubeRay -->|runtime| Ray[Ray 2.9.0+<br/>Managed in Pods]
    KubeRay -->|controller framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.16.3]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    KubeRay -.->|ingress| OpenShiftRoute[OpenShift Route API]
    KubeRay -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano[Volcano v1.6.0-alpha]
    KubeRay -.->|GCS fault tolerance| Redis[External Redis]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ODHOperator[ODH Operator] -->|installs & manages| KubeRay
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes metrics| KubeRay
    ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA] -.->|TLS certs| KubeRay

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|UI management| KubeRay
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|job orchestration| KubeRay

    %% External Services
    KubeRay -->|API access| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    KubeRay -->|image pulls| ContainerRegistry[Container Registry]

    %% Ray Cluster Services (Created by Operator)
    KubeRay -->|creates & manages| RayCluster[Ray Clusters<br/>Head + Workers]
    RayCluster -->|exposes| GCS[Ray GCS<br/>6379/TCP]
    RayCluster -->|exposes| RayDashboard[Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP]
    RayCluster -->|exposes| RayClient[Ray Client<br/>10001/TCP]
    RayCluster -->|exposes| RayServe[Ray Serve<br/>8000/TCP]

    %% Styling
    style KubeRay fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    style K8s fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Ray fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ControllerRuntime fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    style OpenShiftRoute fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Volcano fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Redis fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    style ODHOperator fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceCA fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#82b366,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Integration Points
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Pipelines fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#82b366,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% External Services
    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ContainerRegistry fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Ray Services
    style RayCluster fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style GCS fill:#fff,stroke:#666
    style RayDashboard fill:#fff,stroke:#666
    style RayClient fill:#fff,stroke:#666
    style RayServe fill:#fff,stroke:#666
